---------------------------------------------
Warhammer with Crusher Hit - Nested Macros (Only works as part of nested Macro; First Macro, AttackType, contains the nesting query)
---------------------------------------------
Warhammer-Crusher-Str-AttackType
?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|Warhammer-Crusher-Str-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|Warhammer-Crusher-Str-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|Warhammer-Crusher-Str-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|Warhammer-Crusher-Str-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|Warhammer-Crusher-Str-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|Warhammer-Crusher-Str-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|Warhammer-Crusher-Str-Disadvantage3-Nested}} 
---------------------------------------------
Warhammer-Crusher-Str-Standard-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee Attack - Warhammer&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Warhammer attack .*&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[1d8!cf<1cs>8 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Bludgeoning&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] Bludgeoning + $[[4]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[6]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Crusher Hit= Once per turn, when you hit a creature with an attack that deals bludgeoning damage, you can move it 5 feet to an unoccupied space, provided the target is no more than one size larger than you.&#125;&#125; {{Crusher Crit= When you score a critical hit that deals bludgeoning damage to a creature, attack rolls against that creature are made with advantage until the start of your next turn.&#125;&#125; {{Crusher Crit= When you score a critical hit that deals bludgeoning damage to a creature, attack rolls against that creature are made with advantage until the start of your next turn.&#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------
Warhammer-Crusher-Str-Advantage-Nested
&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee Attack - Warhammer (Advantage)&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Warhammer attackat **Advantage** *&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[2d8!!cf<1cs>8kh1 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Bludgeoning&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] Bludgeoning + $[[4]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[6]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Crusher Hit= Once per turn, when you hit a creature with an attack that deals bludgeoning damage, you can move it 5 feet to an unoccupied space, provided the target is no more than one size larger than you.&#125;&#125; {{Crusher Crit= When you score a critical hit that deals bludgeoning damage to a creature, attack rolls against that creature are made with advantage until the start of your next turn.&#125;&#125;
