&{template:default&#125; {{name=Melee Attack - Warhammer (Disadvantage x3)&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Warhammer attackat **Triple Disadvantage** *&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[4d8!!cf<1cs>8kl1 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[1 [Magic Weapon]]] [Magic Weapon] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Bludgeoning&#125;&#125; {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[3]] Bludgeoning + $[[4]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Crusher Hit= Once per turn, when you hit a creature with an attack that deals bludgeoning damage, you can move it 5 feet to an unoccupied space, provided the target is no more than one size larger than you.&#125;&#125; {{Crusher Crit= When you score a critical hit that deals bludgeoning damage to a creature, attack rolls against that creature are made with advantage until the start of your next turn.&#125;&#125;
---------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------
Warhammer with Magic Weapon and Crusher Hit - Unnested Macros - Works on it's own, but not in a nested query
---------------------------------------------
Warhammer-Crusher-Str-MW-Standard
&{template:default} {{name=Melee Attack - Warhammer}} {{Description=*@{Selected|character_name} makes a Warhammer attack .*}} [[ [[ [[1d8!cf<1cs>8 [Weapon Dice]]] [Weapon Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Strength_mod} [Str]]] [Str] + [[1 [Magic Weapon]]] [Magic Weapon] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Weapon=$[[0]] Bludgeoning}} {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies}} {{Static=$[[3]] Bludgeoning + $[[4]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** }} {{Crusher Hit= Once per turn, when you hit a creature with an attack that deals bludgeoning damage, you can move it 5 feet to an unoccupied space, provided the target is no more than one size larger than you.}} {{Crusher Crit= When you score a critical hit that deals bludgeoning damage to a creature, attack rolls against that creature are made with advantage until the start of your next turn.}}
---------------------------------------------
Warhammer-Crusher-Str-MW-Advantage
